reviewText: I found the video very historical. important, informative and interesting. Every one interested in Ethiopian history and  His Imperial Majesty Emperor Haile Selassie should definitely get a copy.  Thanks to Amazon for making it available..

Apart from the historical information which was seen. the oral information would have been excellent done in English. The  written information and written interpretation of the people being interviewed was very ineligible,and very difficult to read with the fonts way below the readable points at such a speedy flash of the inscriptions. With all that said another attempt of a do over including the above observation it would truly deserve  five stars.
This film tells the story of His Imperial Majesty Emperor Haile Selassie I and his impact on the lives of Ethiopians and Rastafarians. Written and Directed by Tikher Teferra Kidane
